emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mr. and Mrs. Byron Peters and Mr. and Mrs. Harry G. Washington, standing in front of Christmas tree in Redwood Motor Hotel for FROGS Dinner - Dance party
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1970, pg. 15, reads: "Frogs Dinner - Dancing Party Sparks Holiday Season - Pioneer FROGS Byron Peters (left) and Harry G. Washington are the only two active charter members of the prominent male social club. Mrs. Washington admires the necklace that Mrs. Peters received in gift exchange. All Courier Photos by 'Teenie' Harris."
